Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做徒劳的抵抗的不是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让他闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,综合武道五十段的实力 让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是被玩弄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还有秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.18,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,[「キリッ」NETA自DramaCD中夏洛的口頭禪]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密武器是… 这洗杀毁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体大炮小衣炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么小衣非得去当炸弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按下now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊 到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜爱的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗涤物都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这肯定有深远考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人 宝物在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想破坏福尔摩斯侦探学院了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向主公谏言是忠臣的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚森大人 恕我谏言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢对亚森大人出手真是疯了max
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我出手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊 这样根本不像亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想称得上怪盗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是用美丽和智慧来决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被偷来的宝物太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这样不是怪盗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种做法不像美丽的亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不阻止亚森大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉特 托艾特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们发誓向亚森大人效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护亚森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做亚森大人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为此结成的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是怪盗帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些也从今天开始结束了
